{"tid":2402881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門西繞道壽終正寢　政府改道上山又落海CLS","createTime":"2021-02-10T17:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T07:21:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"22c29acf213f2b3a1da6975172ee2b385d9ef719","tid":2402881,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kawaileeFS/posts/440059294010379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FkawaileeFS%2Fposts%2F440059294010379&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=71403f6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kawaileeFS/posts/440059294010379</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnrCGkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnrCGkg.jpg&h=b71e8d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：李家偉 Kawai Lee<br />\n<br />\n【屯門西繞道壽終正寢 政府改道上山又落海CLS】<br />\n<br />\n政府代表今日於會議上表明：將「以屯門繞道取代屯門西繞道」，宣告規劃十餘年、已多次勘探研究的屯門西繞道，整個計劃一夜消失。<br />\n<br />\n屯門區議會交通及運輸委員會今日召開會議，當中除了討論新方案十一號幹線，亦討論到屯門西繞道，而政府代表今日推出名為「屯門繞道」的新方案。<br />\n<br />\n政府代表在會議上指出，「屯門繞道」將以全隧道式興建，雙線雙程，由藍地東交匯處起步，隧道穿過藍地石礦場、大欖郊野公園（鄰近地區）、再經海底隧道穿過青山灣並接入湖山路地底，再接駁到屯赤隧道。代表指，行車距離約11公里，行車時間約8分鐘。當局尚未評估工程造價，預計2036年落成。<br />\n<br />\n先不論工程極為天馬行空，要開山劈石上山下海，貼近屯赤路出口位置的湖山路在工程期間，同時正有港鐵屯門南延綫、湖山公屋兩大工程進行中，恐怕街坊連續廿多年都要在噪音中度過。<br />\n<br />\n我在會議上表明，所有詳細資料未明，絕對不會輕易同意有關個案！同時促請當局公布更多詳情，並要求區議會交運會召開特別會議討論。<br />\n<br />\n新繞道的會議文件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tm/doc/2020_2023/tc/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/20081/ttc_2021_005.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Ftm%2Fdoc%2F2020_2023%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2Fttc%2F20081%2Fttc_2021_005.pdf&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c5113b9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tm/doc/2020_2023/tc/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/20081/ttc_2021_005.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n請各位街坊了解內容，表達意見！"},{"pid":"c7a56dbb3bba3c0caca3acb45d871e02a7641563","tid":2402881,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"廿年後通車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814eebe5c6d4ce4e6651c401bc6cb0fa206778cd","tid":2402881,"uid":82640,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"郁到操炮區就唔肯起<br />\n所以話香港最大發展障礙都係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834f7164898111fe1d4733f2b101a1c7e488b07e","tid":2402881,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"Good丫 咁先夠貴 快快手洗埋d錢佢 等支爆"},{"pid":"78083506bc0a1d3f7987311f636939aca304fc4d","tid":2402881,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"未來廿年超多野起 做工程 fat fat"},{"pid":"664d5842fcb62924a7457f513b9ae72faeb62c07","tid":2402881,"uid":56015,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"814eebe5c6d4ce4e6651c401bc6cb0fa206778cd","tid":2402881,"uid":82640,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"郁到操炮區就唔肯起<br />\n所以話香港最大發展障礙都係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:15:15.000Z","msg":"97之後香港就無運行, 因為中國囉"},{"pid":"181e7dd0438a5ce68ab5a16739913db547e265f3","tid":2402881,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:18:24.000Z","msg":"搞到青山靶場 解放軍地頭喎 會割地俾你香港咩？"},{"pid":"6c362ad530898b110ea6da318b4c800820dd9217","tid":2402881,"uid":126642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"664d5842fcb62924a7457f513b9ae72faeb62c07","tid":2402881,"uid":56015,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"814eebe5c6d4ce4e6651c401bc6cb0fa206778cd","tid":2402881,"uid":82640,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"郁到操炮區就唔肯起<br />\n所以話香港最大發展障礙都係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy